		"Stage by stage comments
	]b
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	[b 
		"Stage 1: The Dream Time:
	]b
	" Standard platforming. The snake above where you starts in just the wrong spot to keep you from jumping over him after getting the boomerang.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	[b 
		"Stage 2: Shark City:
	]b
	" Warp
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	[b 
		"Stage 3: Cliff Edge Corner:
	]b
	" You will start noticing a lot of the 'jump to go down' mechanic here.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	[b 
		"Stage 4: Shark Fin Creek:
	]b
	" Warp cleverly hidden below a breakaway platform.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	[b 
		"Stage 5: Jagged Jungle:
	]b
	" This is the first route change over rchokler's WIP. Standard Platforming.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	[b 
		"Stage 6: One Way Ticket Bridge:
	]b
	" The last stage of the first world. The first and last stages of a world are not choices.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
