	]b
	" Warp
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	[b 
		"Stage 9: The Secret Chamber:
	]b
	" With a secret warp right behind you : )
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	[b 
		"Stage 10: Nightmare Mansion:
	]b
	" Another route change. The kid is JUST able to hit the platform timings.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	[b 
		"Stage 11: The House That Came To Life:
	]b
	" Some standard platforming. A note about the conveyors. They will move you if you aren't moving, but if you are, you still move at normal speed, in both directions, so a pretty poorly implemented mechanic.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	[b 
