	]b
	" Last castle level, something of a switch maze.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	[b 
		"Stage 13: Home Base:
	]b
	" Home Base?
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	[b 
		"Stage 14: Stalactite City:
	]b
	" Ahhh another platform that simply can't be reached, boomerang kid is forced to sit and wait. The alternative level unfortunately is still longer, due to an annoying bat on the route.
	$LF
